snippet.title: Könnte ich EUROFIGHTER fliegen? Zu Besuch im Eurofighter-Simulator! AeroNewsGermany
snippet.description:
Der Eurofighter ist DAS Mehrzweckkampfflugzeug der deutschen Luftwaffe und eines der modernsten und besten Flugzeuge seiner Art. Ultra schnell, ultra flexibel einsetzbar und vor allem ultra wendig. Und technisch und fliegerisch so ziemlich das höchste, was die Luftfahrt zu bieten hat. Ich durfte eine Runde damit fliegen, im Simulator versteht sich, aber im richtigen Simulator im offiziellen Trainingszentrum des Taktischen Luftwaffengeschwaders 73 “Steinhoff” am Fliegerhorst Rostock Laage. snippet.title: Battlefield 6 - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Prepare for the ultimate all-out warfare experience. Here's your look at the Battlefield 6 reveal trailer for the next game in the action FPS series. The Battlefield 6 announcement trailer shows chaos unfolding in cities and more. The trailer also unveils that a multiplayer reveal for Battlefield 6 is coming on July 31, 2025.

Check out the Battlefield 6 trailer's official description, which states, "Witness the vicious path of destruction carved by Pax Armata, the world’s leading private military company. PAX pursues the destruction of NATO and its allies, stopping at nothing to uphold their motto: “Our Protection, Your Peace.”

Lock & load for the ultimate all-out warfare experience. Fight in high-intensity infantry combat. Rip through the skies in aerial dogfights. Demolish your environment for a strategic advantage. In a war of tanks, fighter jets, and massive combat arsenals, your squad is the deadliest weapon. This is Battlefield 6."

#IGN #Battlefield #EA

snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
We’re not done with you. #FNAF2movie in theaters December 5.

--

They’re not just at Freddy’s anymore. 
 
In 2023, Blumhouse’s box-office horror phenomenon Five Nights at Freddy’s, based on the blockbuster game series by Scott Cawthon, became the highest-grossing horror film of the year. Now, a shocking new chapter of animatronic terror begins. 
 
One year has passed since the supernatural nightmare at Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza. The stories about what transpired there have been twisted into a campy local legend, inspiring the town’s first ever Fazfest. 
 
Former security guard Mike (Josh Hutcherson) and police officer Vanessa (Elizabeth Lail) have kept the truth from Mike’s 11-year-old sister, Abby (Piper Rubio), concerning the fate of her animatronic friends. 
 
But when Abby sneaks out to reconnect with Freddy, Bonnie, Chica, and Foxy, it will set into motion a terrifying series of events, revealing dark secrets about the true origin of Freddy’s, and unleashing a long-forgotten horror hidden away for decades.
 
The cast of Five Nights at Freddy’s 2 includes returning co-stars Theodus Crane as Jeremiah and the legendary Matthew Lillard as William Afton. The film features new characters played by Freddy Carter (Shadow and Bone, Pennyworth), Wayne Knight (Jurassic Park, Seinfeld), Mckenna Grace (Ghostbusters franchise, Annabelle Comes Home) and horror icon Skeet Ulrich (Scream, Riverdale). 
 
Five Nights at Freddy’s 2 is directed by acclaimed returning filmmaker Emma Tammi and is written by game series creator Scott Cawthon.
 
The film is produced by Blumhouse founder and CEO Jason Blum and Scott Cawthon, who together produced the first film. The executive producers are director Emma Tammi, Beatriz Sequeira, Christopher Warner, Russell Binder and Marc Mostman. 
 
The first Freddy’s film opened to a record-shattering $80 million in October 2023 and went on to earn almost $300 million worldwide.

The Alien saga expands with Alien: Earth, a new chapter that brings the horror closer to home than ever before. Set in a near-future where Earth is no longer safe, this film explores humanity's final stand against the galaxy’s most terrifying predator.

🧬 What is Alien: Earth About?
Set years after humanity first encountered the Xenomorph threat, Alien: Earth tells the story of what happens when the fight comes to our own planet. After decades of off-world containment, something has gone terribly wrong. A Weyland-Yutani experiment meant to harness the Xenomorph for military use spirals out of control—unleashing the nightmare on Earth’s soil.

snippet.title: Анна Трінчер - Півонії (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
“Півонії” вже на всіх музичних платформах: 
https://annatrincher.fanlink.tv/pivoniji

Apple Music: https://apple.co/46XFc5g

Spotify: https://bit.ly/46XFh94

YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/4o5RP4l


Я мріяла випустити пісню для занять коханням… і обов’язково це зроблю. Але трек «Півонії» - зовсім не про це. Він про набагато глибші історії, емоції та почуття.

Я хочу, щоб ця пісня стала вашим особистим гімном-одою насолоди від себе. Нехай вона зваблює вас… збуджує, розкриває, вдихає у вас життя. Ця пісня - для вас.

І знаєте, коли вам кажуть, що світ не крутиться навколо вас, просто вмикайте «Півонії» і доводьте протилежне ;)

Мені дуже хочеться, щоб цю пісню почуло якомога більше людей, тож мені потрібна ваша допомога! Пишіть про те, що ви відчули після перегляду в коментарях від 7 слів, робіть репост собі в сторіс, а я все бачу, все лайкаю і буду кидати на карту дещо особливе))

And the way you act is usual
Maybe in another world 
I don't feel so unlovable

Would you avoid me or would you look for me too
Tell me is our story through 
Or do our hearts still beat in tune

snippet.title: POIZI & MURAT BOZ - YAPAR MISIN? (OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO)
snippet.description:
Söz&Beste: Poizi (Barış Anaç)
Prod by Dab,Snow 
Mix&Master: JagerStereo
Yapımcı: İsmail Tilaver,Cemal Semetay
Special Thanks EBO
DMC’ye Teşekkürler

Yapar mısın tanışmamış gibi?
Lütfen, şu aklım senden kalmasın.
Bir günah işle, sevabına
Baksın gözlerimden, anlasın.

Ben sende çok yaralandım.
Bir soru sadece:
Nasıl böyle, iyi mi?
Sen kaç kere kaçtın?
Alıştım artık.
Nasıl böyle, iyi mi?
Görmedin gözünle,
Durmadın sözünde.
Ben yokum bu hikâyede,
Belki böyle daha iyidir.

Olmaz öyle, konuşarak yapamayız.
Bugün belli, yarın değil.
O yüzden ye o parayı.
Geç karşıma, otur şöyle.
Neler olmuş öyle, değil mi?
Sana bir kez hayatımı anlatayım.
Denedim hep dayanmayı.
Unutamıyorum desem,
Olur, bütün anılara büyük ayıp.
Hislerim çok kayıp,
Bana cehennemden bir yer ayır.

Of…
İçim eriyor.
İçimde eriyor.
Olmaz öyle artık,
Bizi duyan ne diyor?
Güvenmiyorum sana,
İnkâr ediyordun
Her şeyi güzel yapan da
Zehir ediyor.

snippet.title: Slipknot: 25th Anniversary Edition Deluxe Reissue (Trailer)
snippet.description:
SLIPKNOT: 25TH ANNIVERSARY EDITION will be released on September 5th featuring the Original Studio Album plus 46 bonus tracks (42 of which have never been heard before) including the Indigo Ranch Mixes, Demos/Alternate Mixes, and LIVE performances from 1999-2000.
 
6 LP BOX SET (Limited to 1,999 copies)
• Blood Filled Vinyl – 100 [SOLD OUT]
• Blood Splattered Vinyl – 1,899
 
Pre-order the Box Set + view complete tracklisting now at https://slipknotmerch.com

Listen to the previously unreleased demo of “Prosthetics” here: https://youtu.be/wWpL-L_3Ux8

___
LP 1: SLIPKNOT 
The seminal debut album from Slipknot.
 
LP 2 & 3: INDIGO RANCH MIXES (Box Set Exclusive)
The legendary Indigo Ranch mixes. In 1999 the band gathered at Malibu’s Indigo Ranch to record their breakthrough debut. These early rough mixes showcase the raw energy and chaotic vibe before the final Ross Robinson mixes.
 
LP 4: DEMOS & ALTERNATE MIXES
Side One: Demos - These are the original demos recorded before the band entered Indigo Ranch with Ross Robinson. These demos were then refined in the studio to become the debut album. Some of the actual tracks from the demos were used in the final mixes.
 
Side Two: Jay Baumgardner and Ulrich Wild Mixes - The band and label wanted to have test mixes done before finalizing the album and connected with two other renowned mixers to see what they would do to the mixes. Each has a different take on the tracks.
 
LP 5 & 6: LIVE (Box Set Exclusive)
Months after the debut album, the band took to the road and these live recordings showcase the band’s atmospheric rise from headlining Hartford, Connecticut’s legendary 1200 seat Webster Theater in September of 1999, to playing in front of massive crowds in the UK and Iowa in late 2000.
